ref=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>O método&nbsp;<code><strong>HTMLElement.click()</strong></code>&nbsp;simula o&nbsp;clique do mouse em um elemento.</p>\n\n<p>Quando clique é usado com elementos que o suportam (por exemplo, um dos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> tipos listados acima), ele também dispara evento de clique do elemento que vai propagar&nbsp;pelos&nbsp;elementos mais acima na árvore de documentos (ou cadeia do&nbsp;evento) e disparando&nbsp;seus eventos de clique também. No entanto, o evento de clique, propagado como&nbsp;bubble,&nbsp;não vai iniciar a navegação do elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>&nbsp;como se uma verdadeiro&nbsp;clique do mouse tivesse sido recebido.&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>elt</em>.click()</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificação","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-2651361\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 HTML Specification' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 HTML Specification</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>20<sup>[3]</sup></td>\n   <td>5<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span><sup>[2]</sup></td>\n   <td>6<sup>[3]</sup></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>input@file (limited)</code></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>4</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>12.10</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>input@file (full)</code></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>4</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Antes Gecko 5.0 (Firefox 5.0 / Thunderbird 5.0 / SeaMonkey 2.2), Gecko não implementa&nbsp;o método de clique&nbsp;em outros elementos que podem ser esperados para responder a cliques do mouse como links (elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>), nem seria necessariamente acionado o evento clique de outros elementos.</p>\n\n<p>[2] Em versões do Opera o método <code>click()</code> irá silenciosamente ser ignorado&nbsp;se for&nbsp;realizado baseado no motor de layout Presto em <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> com o atributo&nbsp;type definido para o arquivo e seu CSS <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/display\"><code>display</code></a> propriedade definida como nenhum.</p>\n\n<p>[3] As versões mais antigas tinham <code>HTMLInputElement.click()</code> e <code>HTMLButtonElement.click()&nbsp;</code>apenas.</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"especificação"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"O método HTMLElement.click() simula o clique do mouse em um elemento.","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLElement.click()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLElement.click()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTMLElement.click()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLElement.click()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLElement.click()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element.click","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"HTMLElement.click()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLElement.click()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"HTMLElement.click()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/htmlelement/click","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/htmlelement/click/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement","title":"HTMLElement"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/click","title":"HTMLElement.click()"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLElement.click() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}